The turnover of FARA in 2016 was circa $5 million with 86.4% spent on research grants, 3.7% on education, awareness, and outreach programs, and 1.9% on conferences. FARA hs received a Four Star rating from Charity Navigator for 8 consecutive years.<ref name = "charitynavigator">https://www.charitynavigator.org/index.cfm?bay=search.summary&orgid=12621</ref>
